Class CohortRet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nus.cool.core.cohort.storage.CohortRet

  • public class CohortRet
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for Cohort Analysis Result We consider the Cohort Analysis Result as a x-y Axis x-Axis is age, y-Axis is value, legend is cohort group CohortResult class is generated according to the ageselection.
